invalid type: string "The lake was built to cool the blast furnaces of the steel plant. What was industrial infrastructure has become, over 60 years, an ecology ‚Äî the water attracts birds, the banks have grown trees, and the people of Rourkela use the lake's edge the way people in other cities use parks. The industrial skyline is visible across the water in every direction.", expected f64ˇˇˇˇˇˇˇ